Package: MLBBattingCompare
Type: Package
Title: MLB Player Batting Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xavier Cajigas Rivera
Maintainer: Xavier Cajigas Rivera <xcajigasrivera@usf.edu>
Description: This package offers multiple functions to be able to compare the batting statistics of Major League Baseball players.
    It can retreive the batting average, hits, home runs, runs batted in, slugging percentage, and on base percentage of the players
    within the dataset. Another function can compare those statistics between two players as well as displaying them side by side.
License: CCO
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
